![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1630511075479-4Y044I8OV6WGYIVRJCEX/Burning193.jpg?format=original)

It's a SUPER WEEK on the Major Issues Podcast as we are hyped to talk about the first season of the critically acclaimed series Superman and Lois! No talk about the Man of Steel is complete without a visit from our favorite Kryptonian Tasmin, of the Aspiring Kryptonian Podcast, so she has stopped by to spread the love! Join us as we discuss modern Superman interpretations, get an update on her "Superman Museum", and GUSH over the heart, humor, and spectacle that exists in Superman and Lois Season 1!  

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
